# Personal Overrides

> Rename this file to `CLAUDE.local.md` to activate it. It's gitignored — your settings stay local.

## Local Dev Environment

- Postgres on `localhost:5432`, user `postgres`, password in `.env.local`
- Dev server on port 3000: `pnpm dev`
- Node version pinned via `.nvmrc` — run `nvm use` before starting

## My Preferences

- I prefer concise responses — skip the recap after each change
- When suggesting fixes, show the diff, don't explain what changed
- Use `pnpm` — do not suggest `npm` or `yarn` commands

